John Gabaya, chairman, Bwari Area Council, Federal Capital Territory (FCT), Abuja, has been involved in a ghastly motor accident. Details of the accident are not known as of the time of filing the story. It happened within the Bwari area on Friday. A source told DAILY POST that the chairman has been rushed to an undisclosed hospital for treatment as he sustained injuries on his legs. The chairman is due to be sworn in on 29th May, 2022 for a second term, having won the last council poll under the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP.